QuestData.Title: Stealing the Naga's Secrets
QuestData.Description:
<Upon closer inspection, it becomes clear that the blades have been forged from Azerite.
Weapons of this power should never be in the hands of the naga.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Steal the Azerite weaponry and fight your way out of Zanj'ir Terrace!
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Bring the weapon to Jaina Proudmoore within Deepsea Refuge
